      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a dedicated project or as a source for parts. The engine currently runs roughly and will require significant mechanical attention, possibly a full overhaul, to be roadworthy again. Externally, the body shows heavy wear with significant rust patches, large dents, and a failing paint job. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with several tears and the electronics are inconsistent. This car is sold as-is and will likely need to be towed.",
