      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in truly pristine condition. This specimen has been meticulously maintained to a showroom standard, exhibiting no signs of wear and offering an uncompromising driving experience. From the flawless exterior finish to the factory-fresh interior, every detail reflects a legacy of careful stewardship. This is more than just a pre-owned vehicle; it is an investment-grade example of automotive excellence, ready for the most discerning collector or enthusiast.",
      "price": 48900.0,
