    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Hey there, neighbor! Up for grabs is my absolute pride and joy. I\u2019ve spent more weekends polishing this beauty than I care to admit, and honestly, she still looks and drives like she just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s rare to find one kept in such pristine, collector-grade shape\u2014it really is a total gem. I'm only letting her go to a good home where she'll be truly appreciated. Come take a look, grab a coffee, and let's get you behind the wheel of something special!",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
