    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offering a surgically maintained E92 M3, a true high-revving icon. The S65 V8 has been meticulously cared for, featuring upgraded rod bearings with increased clearances and treated shells to ensure total bottom-end reliability. The DCT gearbox features a bespoke GTS software flash for instantaneous shift-logic and rev-matching precision. Every bushing has been inspected for zero deflection, and the suspension is dialed for neutral turn-in and maximum lateral G-loading. With a factory-spec compression ratio and a pristine underbody free of any fluid migration, this is a turn-key performance machine for the discerning enthusiast who demands peak thermal efficiency and mechanical harmony. This is a concours-level example with a track-honed soul.",
      "price": 48950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
